MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS, EDUCATION AND EXPERIENCE: *
• Any combination of education and experience that has been achieved and is equivalent to the stated education and experience and required knowledge, skills and abilities sufficient to successfully perform the essential duties and responsibilities of this job; OR

• Bachelor’s degree in a Human Resources related field, such as Management, Public
